bundle.name: Qlik Dashboard bundle
bundle.description:
This is a set of supported objects that will facilitate dashboard creation in Qlik Sense: A navigation button, a date picker, a slider, a demand-reporting button and a share button. These can be used in addition to the objects found under "Charts".

For limitations and support conditions, see the documentation.
